name: Utilities-for-pde-toolbox-matlab
tagline: Easy coefficients and geometry for PDE toolbox
body: # Utilities-for-PDE-Toolbox-MATLAB Easy coefficients and geometry for PDE toolbox. There are two sub-projects. *** ## Easy extraction of PDE coefficients View this video to see how the 'pde coefficients' app extracts coefficients for the PDE toolbox. Symbolic Math Toolbox is required. *** ## Easy creation of PDE geometry. Create 2-D geometry for PDE toolbox using convenience classes. Start with this [README](geometry_html/README.html) to see how the classes work.
